<i>Sharingan!</i>

252
00:13:39,246 --> 00:13:40,838
<i>Is that, the Sharingan...?</i>

253
00:13:47,054 --> 00:13:49,852
<i>If this is the same Kekkei Genkai</i>
<i>as Kakashi Sensei's...</i>

254
00:13:50,591 --> 00:13:52,456
<i>he can read Bushy Brow's Jutsu!</i>

255
00:13:53,594 --> 00:13:57,894
<i>Genjutsu or Ninjutsu...</i>
<i>it's some kind of magic either way.</i>

256
00:13:58,632 --> 00:14:00,122
<i>I'll reveal that!</i>

257
00:14:11,979 --> 00:14:15,415
Although you have seen Sasuke
using powerful Jutsu like

258
00:14:16,016 --> 00:14:18,246
Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu,
Demon Wind Shuriken,

259
00:14:18,886 --> 00:14:22,845
Windmill Shadow, and Sharingan,

260
00:14:22,923 --> 00:14:25,118
the greatest of all is...

261
00:14:32,333 --> 00:14:34,426
the sharp look of his eyes!

262
00:14:34,668 --> 00:14:36,693
Any girl who has been stared
at with those eyes,

263
00:14:36,771 --> 00:14:39,501
will fall in love with him!

264
00:14:40,074 --> 00:14:43,407
Sasuke!
Look this way!

265
00:14:44,712 --> 00:14:46,475
You're... annoying.

266
00:14:47,581 --> 00:14:52,314
Well, that cold behavior is also
another attractive quality of Sasuke...

267
00:14:56,056 --> 00:15:00,857
Next is our teacher,
Kakashi Hatake Sensei,

268
00:15:01,028 --> 00:15:04,225
also known as
the Copy Ninja Kakashi.

269
00:15:04,298 --> 00:15:07,426
He uses the Sharingan in his eye
to assess the enemy's technique

270
00:15:07,501 --> 00:15:09,901
and copy over
a thousand Jutsu techniques.

271
00:15:18,546 --> 00:15:22,642
But he's always late to meet people,
and whenever he has any time

272
00:15:22,716 --> 00:15:26,174
he always reads this questionable book
called Make Out Paradise,

273
00:15:26,253 --> 00:15:27,948
and he always looks like he
doesn't really care about things...

274
00:15:28,055 --> 00:15:30,182
Leaf Village Secret Finger Jutsu:

275
00:15:34,128 --> 00:15:35,356
A Thousand Years of Death!

276
00:15:39,266 --> 00:15:43,293
And the biggest mystery of all
is his face hidden under that mask!

277
00:15:43,938 --> 00:15:45,769
I wonder what he really looks like...

278
00:15:53,814 --> 00:15:57,181
Ninja Art, Summoning
Earth Style: Fanged Pursuit Jutsu!

279
00:16:14,201 --> 00:16:17,534
If you can't use your eyes or ears,
simply use your nose.

280
00:16:18,539 --> 00:16:22,134
That's what happens when
you're closing your eyes in the midst of fog.

281
00:16:22,710 --> 00:16:25,907
This is the Summoning Jutsu
specialized for pursuit.

282
00:16:27,748 --> 00:16:31,240
On top of all that, why does he
have the Sharingan in his left eye

283
00:16:31,585 --> 00:16:33,450
that is only passed on in the Uchiha clan?

284
00:16:34,722 --> 00:16:37,054
One mystery after another when
it comes to this person,

285
00:16:37,124 --> 00:16:38,648
so many things that I don't understand...

286
00:16:38,726 --> 00:16:40,193
I should ask him next time
I have the chance.

287
00:16:46,033 --> 00:16:47,159
Lightning Blade!

288
00:16:48,569 --> 00:16:49,399
What the...?!

289
00:16:49,470 --> 00:16:52,803
His hand is...
visibly overflowing with Chakra!

290
00:16:55,809 --> 00:16:57,640
You are too dangerous.

291
00:17:01,148 --> 00:17:02,775
Water Prison Jutsu.

292
00:17:03,150 --> 00:17:03,946
Oh no!

293
00:17:07,021 --> 00:17:07,851
Secret Jutsu.

294
00:17:17,398 --> 00:17:18,865
Crystal Ice Mirrors!

295
00:17:19,466 --> 00:17:23,095
Next up are the Ninjutsu of
the other Ninjas besides us.

296
00:17:23,170 --> 00:17:27,698
There's such a diverse collection of
Ninjutsu that I have no time to explain all...

297
00:17:30,277 --> 00:17:35,214
Chapter of Rivals

298
00:17:36,183 --> 00:17:38,947
Please, Sasuke,
whom I feel is like my future self,

299
00:17:39,019 --> 00:17:40,452
take care of the next part.

300
00:17:42,890 --> 00:17:46,291
Sure. After all, I have to be the one
to do something about it.

301
00:17:47,361 --> 00:17:50,421
I knew that from the beginning.

302
00:17:51,966 --> 00:17:54,628
Don't try so hard to look cool.

303
00:17:54,802 --> 00:17:56,201
Sasuke, the snob.

304
00:17:56,837 --> 00:17:58,566
Don't interfere.

305
00:17:58,772 --> 00:18:00,569
Stay out of it, loser.

306
00:18:00,774 --> 00:18:01,832
Annoying.

307
00:18:02,209 --> 00:18:03,039
Shut up!

308
00:18:03,444 --> 00:18:06,675
I hate the fact that only you stand out.

309
00:18:08,215 --> 00:18:13,346
Nobody strong around you
shows any interest in you.

310
00:18:13,687 --> 00:18:15,086
What the...?!

311
00:18:15,789 --> 00:18:16,778
Just watch this.

312
00:18:17,524 --> 00:18:18,354
Hey!

313
00:18:18,926 --> 00:18:21,759
You there...
What's your name?

314
00:18:22,796 --> 00:18:27,756
I'm Gaara of the desert.
I have an interest in you as well...

315
00:18:28,636 --> 00:18:29,432
What's your name?

316
00:18:30,170 --> 00:18:32,001
Sasuke Uchiha.

317
00:18:32,606 --> 00:18:35,769
Hey, you there.
Identify yourself.

318
00:18:37,778 --> 00:18:41,145
<i>Dang it!</i>
<i>Again? It's always about Sasuke!</i>

319
00:18:41,382 --> 00:18:44,943
When asking someone his name,
give your own name first.

320
00:18:46,987 --> 00:18:48,352
You, with the unpleasant look.

321
00:18:48,822 --> 00:18:49,880
Wait a minute!

322
00:18:55,763 --> 00:18:58,527
Why don't you fight with me here now?

323
00:18:58,899 --> 00:19:01,766
I AM going to take out the Bushy Brow.
Believe it!

324
00:19:02,236 --> 00:19:06,138
The one I want to fight isn't you...
It's Uchiha.

325
00:19:06,507 --> 00:19:08,441
Everybody says Sasuke, Sasuke!
It's annoying!

326
00:19:08,509 --> 00:19:09,476
It's true!

327
00:19:09,677 --> 00:19:12,737
Nobody thinks that you're
the main character leader!

328
00:19:13,280 --> 00:19:16,841
That's not true, they're all just blind!

329
00:19:17,151 --> 00:19:20,348
Huh... As usual you're just about
the talk and not the walk.

330
00:19:20,587 --> 00:19:22,111
That's not true!

331
00:19:22,423 --> 00:19:23,754
Leaf Whirlwind!

332
00:19:26,193 --> 00:19:28,388
See, you are just about the talk.

333
00:19:28,929 --> 00:19:30,260
Uhh... even Sakura is picking on me.

334
00:19:31,598 --> 00:19:35,534
The students who gathered for
this Chunin Exam are all skilled,

335
00:19:35,602 --> 00:19:38,196
and are the cream of the crop...

336
00:19:39,440 --> 00:19:44,605
Shikamaru Nara, Choji Akimichi,
Ino Yamanaka,

337
00:19:45,412 --> 00:19:51,180
Hinata Hyuga, Kiba Inuzuka & Akamaru,
and Shino Aburame...

338
00:19:52,019 --> 00:19:55,386
You won't never be able to win
with the way you have been fighting.

339
00:19:56,156 --> 00:19:57,555
You must understand that, right?

340
00:19:57,758 --> 00:20:00,124
Y-Yeah! Of course!

341
00:20:00,561 --> 00:20:02,495
You, too. Be careful not to let
your guard down

342
00:20:02,563 --> 00:20:04,554
so you won't be defeated
by some lame guy!

343
00:20:04,732 --> 00:20:06,324
Huh! Of course!

344
00:20:11,872 --> 00:20:12,634
That's right...

345
00:20:12,706 --> 00:20:16,904
We passed the first stage
of the Chunin Exam and

346
00:20:17,044 --> 00:20:19,205
are heading to the location
of the second stage...

347
00:20:20,013 --> 00:20:23,107
No matter what kind of adversity
may lie ahead,

348
00:20:23,183 --> 00:20:25,413
we will not be afraid!

349
00:20:25,953 --> 00:20:30,049
And we will pass the exam
to become a Chunin!

350
00:20:30,390 --> 00:20:34,383
Because we... we...

351
00:20:34,628 --> 00:20:37,927
have the greatest teamwork
that was formed by a strong bond!

352
00:20:38,432 --> 00:20:40,297
Okay! Let's go!

353
00:20:48,909 --> 00:20:52,174
Thank you so much for cooperating
with the interview!

354
00:20:52,479 --> 00:20:54,470
- Thank you...
- Leader!

355
00:20:54,648 --> 00:20:56,206
Do your best!

356
00:20:56,450 --> 00:20:58,179
Yeah leave it to me!

357
00:20:58,452 --> 00:21:00,352
- Bye!
- See you!

358
00:21:00,487 --> 00:21:02,648
- Do your best!
- Good luck!

359
00:21:04,752 --> 00:21:09,348
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

360
00:21:09,456 --> 00:21:17,556
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

361
00:21:18,632 --> 00:21:27,165
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

362
00:21:27,775 --> 00:21:35,477
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

363
00:21:36,884 --> 00:21:42,413
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

364
00:21:42,489 --> 00:21:46,255
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

365
00:21:46,327 --> 00:21:49,888
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

366
00:21:50,364 --> 00:21:58,772
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

367
00:21:59,173 --> 00:22:04,236
<i>when you want to cry, and you want to run away</i>

368
00:22:04,311 --> 00:22:08,714
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

369
00:22:08,883 --> 00:22:12,546
<i>Just sing.</i>

370
00:22:12,853 --> 00:22:17,950
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

371
00:22:18,092 --> 00:22:20,219
<i>The two are one</i>

372
00:22:20,327 --> 00:22:26,596
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

373
00:22:27,201 --> 00:22:32,195
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

374
00:22:37,511 --> 00:22:40,912
The 44th Training Field,
also known as the Forest of Death.

375
00:22:41,215 --> 00:22:43,547
From here on it's a serious battle
between the Ninjas,

376
00:22:43,617 --> 00:22:44,743
anything could happen!

377
00:22:45,386 --> 00:22:47,616
It's going down in earnest now!

378
00:22:49,189 --> 00:22:51,282
This is getting interesting!

379
00:22:51,525 --> 00:22:53,584
A life risking survival game in the forest!

380
00:22:53,827 --> 00:22:55,522
I will survive without fail!

381
00:22:56,263 --> 00:22:59,960
Next time: "The Chunin Exam Stage 2:
The Forest of Death!

382
00:23:00,100 --> 00:23:02,398
As for me, I'm going to kick butt again!
